snippet.title: Iron Roads Pre-release Trailer
snippet.description:
Lay tracks, buy trains, set their routes. Optimise your network and repeat till dawn. 

Run your enterprise efficiently while avoiding backlogs, jams, bankruptcy or angry passengers, and you'll be recognised for the unsung train hero you know you are.

Wishlist or play the demo now on https://store.steampowered.com/app/2171550/Iron_Roads/
